'''Ronto Clan''' was an [[Jedi Initiate/Legends|initiate]] training clan of the [[New Jedi Order]], named after the [[Ronto/Legends|ronto]], a creature native to [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. In [[35 ABY/Legends|35 ABY]], it consisted mostly of students who were the between the ages of eight-to-ten.

